OL,6,FA mother bereaved twice by suicide has
OL,7,Flaunched a website to help other
OL,8,Fpeople affected by it and tackle the
OL,9,Fstigma.
OL,11,FKaren Sykes' husband, Ian, and
OL,12,Fdaughter, Beth, both took their own
OL,13,Flives within four years of each other.
OL,15,FShe's now launched 'Speak Their Name'
OL,16,Fwith Anna Scott from Haworth, whose
OL,17,Fdaughter, Ellen, also died by suicide.
