OL,3,CMum who lost daughter and husband to
OL,4,Csuicide campaigns to help others
OL,6,FThe website allows people to create
OL,7,Fpersonalised remembrance pages for
OL,8,Ftheir loved ones, while also providing
OL,9,Fa platform for connection and support
OL,10,Fwith other people who have experienced
OL,11,Fsimilar loss.
OL,13,FKaren Sykes said: "Being bereaved by
OL,14,Fsuicide can be the loneliest feeling
OL,15,Fin the world.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
