OL,3,CMum who lost daughter and husband to
OL,4,Csuicide campaigns to help others
OL,6,F"Often even close friends don't know
OL,7,Fwhat to say; and sometimes, they are
OL,8,Fso afraid of saying the wrong thing
OL,9,Fthat they say nothing at all, and this
OL,10,Fleads to an even greater sense of
OL,11,Fisolation.
OL,13,F"Speak Their Name is helping
OL,14,Findividuals like me feel connected
OL,15,Fwith others who have also experienced
OL,16,Floss by suicide, encouraging us to
OL,17,Fnavigate our grief with greater self-
OL,18,Fcompassion."
