OL,4,Csuicide campaigns to help others
OL,6,FAnna Scott said: "People will have a
OL,7,Fpage that they dedicate to someone
OL,8,Fthey've lost to suicide, which is like
OL,9,Fa memorial page.
OL,11,F"They're able to submit a video, they
OL,12,Fare able to submit some wording about
OL,13,Fthat person, and some photographs and
OL,14,Falso a square which is not of that
OL,15,Fperson, but it represents that person."
OL,17,FBut it's also a platform to raise
OL,18,Fawareness, with those bereaved by
OL,19,Fsuicide at a higher risk of taking
OL,20,Ftheir own life.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
