OL,3,CMum who lost daughter and husband to
OL,4,Csuicide campaigns to help others
OL,6,FKaren says the website highlights the
OL,7,F'urgent need for accessible support
OL,8,Ffor those bereaved by suicide', after
OL,9,Fa survey showed that over a third of
OL,10,Fthose bereaved were unaware of
OL,11,Favailable help, and 60% did not access
OL,12,Fany support despite their increased
OL,13,Fsuicide risk.
OL,15,FShe added: "When you look at those
OL,16,Fpages, they are unique people, they
OL,17,Fare a person in their own being, with
OL,18,Ftheir own unique characteristics and
OL,19,Ftheir death shouldn't be defining
OL,20,Fthem."
